		<descript>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
			<abstract>Madrid Orthoimagery, 2006 is a set of digital orthophotos representing Madrid, Spain. The dataset is comprised of eleven tiles; the photos were taken in 2005 and have a 60 centimeter resolution. </abstract>
			<purpose>Orthophotos serve a variety of purposes for both display and analysis. This dataset is for non-commercial research purposes only.</purpose>
		</descript>
